[{"Code":"en","Title":"Prohibited and High Risk Industries & Regions","Slug":"prohibited-and-high-risk-industries-and-countries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote data-block-id=\"mfm4t34d-z6w96q-044\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm4t7tw-ap200g-046\"> Guidelines:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mfm4ti63-q0vhae-047\"><li data-block-id=\"mfm4ti63-9vwpp8-048\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm4t34e-b4x689-045\"><strong><u>For high-risk industries</u></strong>, merchants will go through an additional process and be required to provide additional documents as part of due diligence (e.g., a sectoral license).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mfm4ti63-9vwpp8-048\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm4t34e-b4x689-045\"><strong><u>For high-risk countries</u>,</strong> merchants will go through an additional process for onboarding.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mfm4ti63-9vwpp8-048\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm4t34e-b4x689-045\"><strong><u>For prohibited industries and countries</u>,</strong> merchants are <strong>not allowed to onboard.</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mfm4ti63-9vwpp8-048\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mfm4t34e-b4x689-045\"><strong><u>Xendit Group</u></strong> collectively refers to all our entities and markets.</p></li></ul></blockquote><hr class=\"page-break-line\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-page-break=\"true\" style=\"break-after:page;\"><h4 data-block-id=\"mfkqvt2m-r4y4mw-012\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family:Inter;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align: